  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to evaluate middle term compliance (≥ 2 years) of the Mandibular
      Advancement Devices Tali® in patients with Syndrome of Obstructive Sleep Apnea and Hypopneas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
